1. orphaned items in held POs card needs to indicate which supplier the item belongs to
2. modals in restock management, they change size depending on content, however it is better if the modals have one fixed max size with enough padding to cover all content, they should only resize based on screen size and view port, not based on content
3. in the current requests tab for restock management, the supplier cards that have requests that should have order placed status, those supplier cards should also show that they are linked to a PO with order placed (right now only the requests cards get that status badge)
4. the print dialogue is not opening for purchase orders, it now gets an error that popups are blocked by the browser, it should be able to be done without using a popup to avoid cases where there may be a popup blocker which is very common hence use another method.